Heap's algorithm generates all possible permutations of N objects.

heaps_algorithm.c recursive implementation
heaps_algo_nonrecur non recursive implementation

Compile the code
~$ gcc -o heaps_algorithm heaps_algorithm.c
~$ gcc -o heaps_algo_nonrecur heaps_algo_nonrecur.c

Usage. This will ouptut all the possible permuations
~$ ./heaps_algorithm 1 2 3
1 2 3 
2 1 3 
3 1 2 
1 3 2 
2 3 1 
3 2 1

~$ ./heaps_algo_nonrecur 1 2 3
1 2 3 
2 1 3 
3 1 2 
1 3 2 
2 3 1 
3 2 1
